{"tid":433731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"少女遭魔女黨集體欺凌　慘被扯上衣剝底褲","createTime":"2017-10-12T15:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T13:18:49.000Z","uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"551e365acebc260c01d2ef84de92c365451d999a","tid":433731,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"少女遭魔女黨集體欺凌　慘被扯上衣剝底褲<br />\n10月12日(四)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短片顯示，一名少女慘遭魔女黨集體欺凌。(互聯網)<br />\nWhatsApp群組下午流傳一段令人髮指片段，一名少女慘遭魔女黨集體欺凌，被掌摑最少10巴，更慘遭扯起上衣，受害少女不停呼叫，魔女黨不但未有停手，更變本加厲，脫去少女短褲及內褲，露出衞生巾，整個過程被人拍攝下來，暫未知案件是否在香港發生，惟各人均說廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n東網傍晚接獲讀者提供片段，稱WhatsApp群組中午開始流傳該段魔女黨虐打少女片，相信事發於一處梯間，估計魔女黨最少有4名成員，其中3人集體毆打1名女受害人，1人則負責拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n片中所見，魔女黨首領首先連續掌摑受害少女數巴，另一魔女黨成員亦上前，再掌摑多數巴，首領大叫「躝過嚟、躝過嚟」，然後強行扯起受害少女的上衣，受害少女拉着上衣不放，首領大叫「放手、放手」，終扯起受害少女上衣，並露出乳房，此時其他成員嘩聲四起。<br />\n<br />\n雖然受害少女不停哭泣，說「對唔住、對唔住」，但魔女黨成員並未罷休，強行拖行受害少女，更企圖剝去其短褲，受害少女不停說：「唔好解褲、唔好解褲呀」，但魔女黨成員則說「解咗佢」，雖然有部分成員反對，但其他成員仍不理會，除連續掌摑少女數巴外，更繼續強行脫去受害少女的短褲，最終更脫去內褲，並扯掉受害少女的衞生巾，然後圍着大笑。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科表示，網絡安全及科技罪案調查科正了解及跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171012/bkn-20171012194450703-1012_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171012%2Fbkn-20171012194450703-1012_00822_001.html&d=8nx%2BPB6fXn8UCiGc1HdqQi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=27ab465a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171012/bkn-20171012194450703-1012_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   痴撚線"},{"pid":"7c585c399774e776347e5fd61baff8aae948efb9","tid":433731,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf756894073ad53269142fb7a4b6c7900ea3a744","tid":433731,"uid":147445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0b59e6bce25e9886b0838c6d87ead01b527b4a","tid":433731,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n欺凌依樣野  真係 N 年嚟都 keep 住發生    唔會有一個年代係無 <br />\n人性果然醜惡"},{"pid":"33b9028769ad2fe9d5dcfe1cd75533b2b731a8e3","tid":433731,"uid":21488,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"人地都有老豆老母生<br />\n點解可以咁樣對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f7c5815b1df4a7842a096323c59d1d69f99416","tid":433731,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"片呢？"},{"pid":"54054026a9a985447586de465e857af95a719514","tid":433731,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街 呢啲人捉左實唔可以當佢兒童咁判罪"},{"pid":"516939b987eebbc4103adf8e8e1008a7d5a7cdf3","tid":433731,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"可惜冇<br />\n起底組　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3242b82a431e2dfd490b31baa548934c2bae83","tid":433731,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7bd77a69daa23547fa207b1ec22b6ceef8dcf9","tid":433731,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"呢個年頭仲有人玩欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed99a653dfe0e5e41370580a87f4d7087af471d","tid":433731,